ick completes one bounded, verifiable slice only.\n    70\t- Always validate syntax and package builds after code changes.\n    71\t- Always sync export repo changes back to the mirror workspace when behavior changes.\n    72\t- Always append an evolution note in `.claude/plans/loloop/`.\n    73\t- Update this active plan when milestone focus changes.\n    74\t\n    75\t## Immediate Next Slice Queue\n    76\t1. T / S / M / L density normalization pass\n    77\t2. Needs Human occupancy and collapse behavior pass\n    78\t3. Board interaction polish and guardrails pass\n    79\t4. Drag smoothness micro-polish pass\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
